    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This F87 M2 represents a pinnacle of modern analog performance, powered by the N55B30T0 3.0L TwinPower Turbo inline-six. Mated to a crisp 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain provides 365hp and 343 lb-ft of torque, with an overboost function reaching 369 lb-ft. The chassis is factory-equipped with the Active M Differential and forged aluminum suspension components from the M3/M4, ensuring exceptional lateral grip and turn-in response. Maintenance is up to date, including a recent cooling system refresh and synthetic oil service. The vehicle exhibits minor cosmetic patina consistent with its mileage, but the powertrain and subframe remain in excellent operational health for the discerning driver.",
